title: Week 3 Recap: The College Football Playoff Picture is Wide Open
itunes:title: Week 3 Recap: The College Football Playoff Picture is Wide Open
description:
Jboy breaks down a stacked week 3 in college football. Jake tells you why he thinks Texas A&M still can't hang with Alabama (8:40), how Matt Corral is building his Heisman resume (18:30) and breaking down Auburn's loss to Penn State (28:00) Make sure to check us out LIVE on Youtube every day at 3pm EST, plus follow us @thejboyshow on all social media platforms!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
